@startuml Leader Recruiter Dashboard - Single Flow

title Get Company Dashboard - Single Flow

actor Leader
participant UI
participant API
participant Service
database DB

Leader -> UI : Open dashboard
UI -> API : GET /company-dashboard
API -> Service : GetCompanyDashboard()

Service -> Service : Check permission

Service -> DB : Get staff + activities
DB --> Service : Data

Service -> Service : Calculate metrics

Service --> API : Dashboard DTO
API --> UI : JSON response
UI --> Leader : Display dashboard

note right of Service
  Calculations:
  • Jobs posted/closed
  • Candidates approved
  • Interviews completed
  • Approval rates
  • Top performers
end note

@enduml





